Abstract = {The COVID-19 pandemic required healthcare organizations to rapidly
   upskill workers to care for critically ill patients. An integrative
   review focused on the upskilling of nurses during the pandemic
   identified themes of strategies, benefits, and challenges of rapid
   upskilling. Understanding the effectiveness, satisfaction, and
